      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Pilts's rooftop allies from the playhouse days — they dispose of his corpses (eating the choice bits, stashing the rest across the Shingles; the headless state of recent deliveries doesn't bother them). Six nest in the palace attic (C7).</p><p><strong>Tactics:</strong> lurk in rafter-shadow; strike the moment someone opens the door from outside, or 3 rounds after intruders start moving within. Fight to the death.</p>",
